# Telegram Mini App Rules

## Authentication Source

Telegram Mini App SDK

## Requirements

- Validate initData
- Validate Telegram signature
- Auto create user
- Auto update profile data

## Store

- telegram_id
- username
- first_name
- last_name
- photo_url

## Never use

- Email Login
- Password Login
- Google Login

## Seller Contact

### Display

- Telegram Username

### Contact Button

`https://t.me/{username}`

Always trust Telegram identity as the primary user identity.
